  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Design: Observational - Cross study with followed up for 30 days. The Primary Objective is to
      realize a record that reflects a national overview of the role of cardiac catheterization in
      patients with congenital heart disease in hospitals distributed by geographic density of each
      region of Brazil.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients admitted in the hemodynamic sector with diagnosed or suspected congenital
      cardiopathy and undergoing diagnostic or therapeutic cardiac catheterization. Participants
      release the data in (e-CRF) electronics system. Sample: 2000 records.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
